Full Description: Guardian Watch is the first mobile app that lets you use your smartphone camera to report an emergency.  Guardian Watch is a free app that lets you send alerts and warnings in real time to public safety, your neighbors, and more... live from the scene. Your GPS tells them exactly where they need to go to help. At Guardian Watchâ„¢, our mission is to save lives around the world through visual awareness. With Guardian Watch, you can capture and report emergencies in real time, all from your phone. Send live-stream video to our secure website, provide your exact GPS location and alert 911 and local law enforcement, friends, family, and neighbors of your situation. With Guardian Watch, you also connect through social networking by creating community network groups with whom you can share alerts designed for individuals, neighborhood watch groups, campus security, and other civic crime watch organizations. You will also find tips and guides to help you prepare in advance for emergency situations. Your home is your castle, your neighborhood is your kingdom, and you want to be safe where you live. Guardian Watch can help bring your community together to create a safe and protected environment.  Guardian Watch is a free service to the public and offers the following key features: Instant Alerts: Notify public safety emergency services and your neighbors in seconds. GPS Location: Feel at ease with Guardian Watch and our GPS location system. Monitoring professionals will be able to find your location when GPS is active. Live-Stream Video: A first for emergency apps, use your smartphone camera to live-stream video of your situation to monitoring public safety and first responders giving them a visual of the scene before they get there; simultaneous two way text messaging with emergency services while live-streaming video to receive directions and provide more intelligence. Reports: Document your situation, journal your story, send group emails, and post links on Facebook and Twitter to stay connected. Great for documentation purposes as well as to inform your neighborhood and crime watch groups with minute-to-minute updates.  Profiles: Organize your neighborhood and/or campus into a watch or public safety group. Send invitations and connect with local public safety authorities to keep on top of important local information ensuring you, your family and your community is well prepared for any event.   Safety Guides: Find vital information and resources designed to help prepare you for emergencies and natural disasters. Our Safety Guides provide the latest and most recent resources, so when an emergency strikes, you are prepared.  To learn more about Guardian Watch, please visit : http://guardianwatch.com

Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: Hours: Mon - Sun 11am - 7pm Payment Methods: cash, check, credit cards Description: Large things always start small. Moshe Schwartz didn't know that his little mattress workshop in Jaffa of 1948 would turn into the largest furniture group in Israel. When his son, Abraham, joined the business in 1956 he purchased new manufacturing machines, increased sales and distribution and coined the name AMINACH (My People Rest). In 1965, AMINACH moved into producing technologically advanced spring mattresses, beds and bedroom furniture and has since then been the largest manufacturer and distributor of furniture in Israel. The Good Night chain target the mid level market segment and the bargain and "Sales" hunters.  The American Comfort chain specializes in imported recliners and living room sets. If you have credit and want immediate gratification and the content is legally downloable via the internet, we want to be your source. And, we want to do it right away, and easily for you. We believe we have the LOWEST price for eBooks on the internet. Since our website is totally automated and you download immediately once payment is approved, there is no shipping. If you find lower prices for eBooks on the internet, write us and we'll investigate. We want to be the Best Price. ContentRealtime offers several values to our users: 1. You can search and find downloadable content across multiple categories and suppliers in one easy to use website. (the "Orbitz" effect) Simply type a word or phrase into the SEARCH BOX on the home page and hit SEARCH button. We take major credit cards via secure PayPal. 2. You can refer friends and earn money for doing so. You do this by sending a friend an email invitation, either to a specific content item or a general "please join". When they register with ContentRealtime, we will log the fact that YOU referred them, and will track and you will earn a percentage of any amounts they spend through our website. The percentage is small, up to our discretion, and during beta is basically "Monopoly money" until we figure out the best way to incent you this way. This amount will be tallied and you can view it at any time under "your account". We reserve the right to forward this amount to you by check or cash, offset future purchases, or find other ways to give you the value you earned by referring friends. (the "make money referring my friends to this site effect---aka Amway MLM effect). Simply INVITE a friend in the lower left portion of any webpage. Once they are invited and accept your invitation, we record that and track earnings for you, look on MY PROFILE on your account page to see this. 3. You can upload your own downloable content to our site, and offer it for sale. We split the proceeds of any sale with you 50/50. You MUST own the content you are uploading (either you created the content yourself, OR, you must have both the "I own" and the "I can sell this downloadable content without any restraints or copyright issues or issues where someone else has an entitlement to either content or the value transaction you are creating by selling it via ContentRealtime") (the "eBay" effect). Just UPLOAD any original content that you own and have the rights to sell and set a price for it. We track the sale, the fact that it is yours and send you 50 percent of the income once received from a fellow downloader. Hit the "UPLOAD content" box next to search or visit the YouContent category. 4. You can vote on content (use the star system) and you can comment and form communities here around the content you like. The FORUM link for community comments is on the lower right side of the main page. (the "social" effect). Go to the FORUM choice in the lower right of the screen, contribute to one of the already started FORUM topics or create your own. Also, you can VOTE on any content item when you are viewing the detail page about that content. Voting and buying content moves that content UP on the most popular and most recent tabs so others will benefit from your interests. FORUM topics can be a single content item (put the node link from that content item HINT: this means copy the browser address of the particular content item you are blogging about into your FORUM post and title the FORUM TOPIC so other users will find your comment and comment on your comment. We appreciate your interests. Thanks for your patronage and input to make this site more useful. We are focused on customer service and want you to have an enjoyable experience that allows you to consume content and become a better person and have fun! Send comments via the Contact Me form on the website or email contactus@contentrealtime.com To start using the site you can: SIGN IN (to register and get newsletters and invite friends and make purchases) HOME page button upper left or HIT any category button on the top row like eBooks, Movies, Games, etc. Enjoy and thank you for visiting our site!
